  "principles": [
    "the server owns product versions eligibility price terms authority and rollout state",
    "the client renders an eligible product and sends registered commands",
    "configuration composes only capabilities already registered and production-ready",
    "one offering version targets one compatible profile family so route terms evidence and wording remain authoritative",
    "new money regulated integration evidence or irreversible capability requires development first",
    "one admin role cannot create fund approve and publish a high-risk offering",
    "recipient personal data is not exported from the eligibility resolver"
